title: 247: Scouting the next great NFL running backs
itunes:title: 247: Scouting the next great NFL running backs
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the next wave of college running backs set to take the NFL by storm (34:44). The guys also review the Falcons huge win over the Buccaneers on Monday Night Football (1:14). DJ and Bucky broke down film from Nick Foles and Aaron Rodgers this past weekend as well (6:58).
